#: ../../Ch01/Ch01_WhyStats_3.rst:58
msgid ""
"Remarkably, most departments had a *higher* rate of admissions for females "
"than for males! Yet the overall rate of admission across the university for "
"females was *lower* than for males. How can this be? How can both of these "
"statements be true at the same time?"
msgstr ""
